            },
            {
              "language": "en",
              "text": "The company will transport the furniture tomorrow."
            },
            {
              "language": "fa",
              "text": "شرکت فردا مبلمان را حمل می‌کند."
            },
            {
              "language": "kmr",
              "text": "Şîrket sibê mobîlyayan vediguhêze."
